Achilles heels
<COREF ID="7" TYPE="IDENT">" National sovereignty "</COREF> is reflected in a country 's ability to engage in diplomatic relations , but in <COREF ID="7" TYPE="IDENT">this most critical area for national survival</COREF> , <COREF ID="19" TYPE="IDENT">Taiwan</COREF> has long been suffering from <COREF ID="28" TYPE="IDENT">PRC</COREF> efforts to undercut <COREF ID="19" TYPE="IDENT">Taiwan 's</COREF> international status .
