" In fact , in recent years <COREF ID="26" TYPE="IDENT">the PRC</COREF> has spent much larger sums of money than <COREF ID="14" TYPE="IDENT">Taiwan</COREF> in trying to woo away <COREF ID="18" TYPE="IDENT"><COREF ID="14" TYPE="IDENT">the ROC 's</COREF> diplomatic partners</COREF> .
